    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me every single day. Whether you're just commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car handles beautifully and is totally ready for its next adventure! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and see it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
