    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and style without the new-car price tag. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, showing only the minor, expected road wear of a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the seats provide excellent support and the carpets are free of significant stains. All dashboard controls, power windows, and the premium audio system are fully functional. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a recent full synthetic oil change and a new air filter. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and the braking system feels firm and responsive. With a clean title in hand and a recent professional detailing, this car is prepared for immediate daily use. It offers a refined driving experience that truly belies its age.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
